As a workaround, you can mark the nested entries as modified manually:

```C#
var nestedJson = context.Entry(blog).ComplexProperty(b => b.NestedJson);
var items = nestedJson.ComplexCollection(j => j.Items);

items[0].State =  EntityState.Modified;
items[1].State =  EntityState.Modified;
items[2].State =  EntityState.Added;
```

If you delete an item you can mark it like this:
```C#
items.GetOriginalEntry(1).State = EntityState.Deleted
```

